channel.title: Server help, the best helper gets admin/co owner
channel.description:
Hey guys :) A day i could use my server on no-ip and everyone could join, now i cant use no-ip and nobody can join, i can only use 192.168.0.100 but none can join..
Ive portforwarded with pfconfig from portforward.com
What shall i do=(

item.title: Server help, the best helper gets admin/co owner
item.dc:creator: @the_reaper77 the reaper77
item.description:
@the_reaper77 wrote:

Are you sure your no-ip server ip wasnt delete? because no-ip deletes ip’s if theres a long time of inactivity from it.

Read full topic
